    Interface UnchainedCore

    interface UnchainedCore {
        bulkImporter: BulkImporter;
        modules: Modules;
        options: ModuleOptions;
        services: {
            bookmarks: {
                migrateBookmarks: (
                    ...args: [
                        {
                            countryCode: string;
                            fromUserId: string;
                            shouldMerge: boolean;
                            toUserId: string;
                        },
                    ],
                ) => Promise;
            };
            enrollments: {
                activateEnrollment: (...args: [enrollment: Enrollment]) => Promise;
                createEnrollmentFromCheckout: (
                    ...args: [
                        order: Order,
                        {
                            context: { deliveryContext?: any; paymentContext?: any };
                            items: { orderPosition: OrderPosition; product: Product }[];
                        },
                    ],
                ) => Promise;
                initializeEnrollment: (
                    ...args: [
                        enrollment: Enrollment,
                        params: { orderIdForFirstPeriod?: string; reason: string },
                    ],
                ) => Promise;
                processEnrollment: (
                    ...args: [
                        initialOrder: Order,
                        orderTransactionContext: {
                            comment?: string;
                            deliveryContext?: any;
                            nextStatus?: OrderStatus;
                            paymentContext?: any;
                        },
                    ],
                ) => Promise;
                terminateEnrollment: (enrollment: Enrollment) => Promise<any>;
            };
            files: {
                createDownloadStream: (...args: [{ fileId: string }]) => Promise;
                createSignedURL: (
                    ...args: [{ directoryName: string; fileName: string; meta?: any }],
                ) => Promise;
                linkFile: (
                    ...args: [{ fileId: string; size?: number; type?: string }],
                ) => Promise;
                removeFiles: (...args: [{ fileIds: string[] }]) => Promise;
                uploadFileFromStream: (
                    ...args: [
                        { directoryName: string; meta?: any; rawFile: any } & Record<
                            string,
                            any,
                        >,
                    ],
                ) => Promise;
                uploadFileFromURL: (
                    ...args: [
                        {
                            directoryName: string;
                            fileInput: {
                                fileId?: string;
                                fileLink: string;
                                fileName: string;
                                headers?: Record<string, unknown>;
                            };
                            meta?: any;
                        },
                    ],
                ) => Promise;
            };
            filters: {
                invalidateFilterCache: (...args: []) => Promise;
                loadFilterOptions: (
                    ...args: [
                        filter: Filter,
                        params: {
                            forceLiveCollection: boolean;
                            productIdSet: Set<string>;
                            searchQuery: SearchQuery;
                        },
                    ],
                ) => Promise;
                loadFilters: (
                    ...args: [
                        searchQuery: SearchQuery,
                        { forceLiveCollection: boolean; productIds: string[] },
                    ],
                ) => Promise;
                searchAssortments: (
                    ...args: [
                        searchQuery: SearchQuery,
                        { forceLiveCollection?: boolean; locale: Locale },
                    ],
                ) => Promise;
                searchProducts: (
                    ...args: [
                        searchQuery: SearchQuery,
                        { forceLiveCollection?: boolean; locale: Locale },
                    ],
                ) => Promise;
            };
            orders: {
                calculateDiscountTotal: (
                    ...args: [order: Order, orderDiscount: OrderDiscount],
                ) => Promise;
                checkoutOrder: (
                    ...args: [
                        orderId: string,
                        transactionContext: {
                            comment?: string;
                            deliveryContext?: any;
                            nextStatus?: OrderStatus;
                            paymentContext?: any;
                        },
                    ],
                ) => Promise;
                confirmOrder: (
                    ...args: [
                        order: Order,
                        transactionContext: {
                            comment?: string;
                            deliveryContext?: any;
                            nextStatus?: OrderStatus;
                            paymentContext?: any;
                        },
                    ],
                ) => Promise;
                createManualOrderDiscount: (
                    ...args: [{ code: string; order: Order }],
                ) => Promise;
                discountedEntities: (
                    ...args: [order: Order, orderDiscount: OrderDiscount],
                ) => Promise;
                findOrInitCart: (
                    ...args: [{ countryCode: string; orderId?: string; user: User }],
                ) => Promise;
                initCartProviders: (...args: [order: Order]) => Promise;
                migrateOrderCarts: (
                    ...args: [
                        {
                            countryCode: string;
                            fromUserId: string;
                            shouldMerge: boolean;
                            toUserId: string;
                        },
                    ],
                ) => Promise;
                nextUserCart: (
                    ...args: [
                        {
                            countryCode: string;
                            forceCartCreation?: boolean;
                            orderNumber?: string;
                            user: User;
                        },
                    ],
                ) => Promise;
                processOrder: (
                    ...args: [
                        initialOrder: Order,
                        orderTransactionContext: {
                            comment?: string;
                            deliveryContext?: any;
                            nextStatus?: OrderStatus;
                            paymentContext?: any;
                        },
                    ],
                ) => Promise;
                registerPaymentCredentials: (
                    ...args: [paymentProviderId: string, paymentContext: PaymentContext],
                ) => Promise;
                rejectOrder: (
                    ...args: [
                        order: Order,
                        transactionContext: {
                            comment?: string;
                            deliveryContext?: any;
                            nextStatus?: OrderStatus;
                            paymentContext?: any;
                        },
                    ],
                ) => Promise;
                supportedDeliveryProviders: (
                    ...args: [params: DeliveryContext],
                ) => Promise;
                supportedPaymentProviders: (...args: [params: PaymentContext]) => Promise;
                supportedWarehousingProviders: (
                    ...args: [params: WarehousingContext],
                ) => Promise;
                updateCalculation: (...args: [orderId: string]) => Promise;
            };
            products: {
                removeProduct: (...args: [{ productId: string }]) => Promise;
                simulateProductDispatching: (
                    ...args: [
                        { product: Product; quantity?: number; referenceDate?: Date },
                    ],
                ) => Promise;
                simulateProductInventory: (
                    ...args: [{ product: Product; referenceDate?: Date }],
                ) => Promise;
                simulateProductPricing: (
                    ...args: [
                        pricingContext: {
                            configuration?: ProductConfiguration[];
                            countryCode: string;
                            currencyCode: string;
                            product: Product;
                            quantity: number;
                            user: User;
                        },
                    ],
                ) => Promise;
            };
            quotations: {
                fullfillQuotation: (
                    ...args: [quotation: Quotation, info: any],
                ) => Promise;
                processQuotation: (
                    ...args: [
                        initialQuotation: Quotation,
                        params: { quotationContext?: any },
                    ],
                ) => Promise;
                proposeQuotation: (
                    ...args: [quotation: Quotation, { quotationContext?: any }],
                ) => Promise;
                rejectQuotation: (
                    ...args: [quotation: Quotation, { quotationContext?: any }],
                ) => Promise;
                verifyQuotation: (
                    ...args: [quotation: Quotation, { quotationContext?: any }],
                ) => Promise;
            };
            users: {
                deleteUser: (...args: [{ userId: string }]) => Promise;
                migrateUserData: (
                    userIdBeforeLogin: string,
                    userId: string,
                ) => Promise<void>;
                updateUserAvatarAfterUpload: (...args: [{ file: File }]) => Promise;
            };
            warehousing: {
                ercMetadata: (
                    ...args: [
                        { locale: Locale; product: Product; token: TokenSurrogate },
                    ],
                ) => Promise;
            };
        };
    }
